children.text: MAKING ESTATE PLANNING SIMPLE, SMART & ACCESSIBLE
Easily plan and share your estate, recieve useful insights of your current estate plan and real time solutions to loopholes identified.
What Features Do we Have Currently?
Access to a summary of your current estate plan
Recieve alerts on possible gaps in your estate plan
Get personalised solutions on identified gaps in your estate plan
Share your estate plan one person
Sorted in simple manner and folders, get access to all your family and financial information. In a neatly created dashboard, get insights into your finances in one place!
